1
00:00:01,100 --> 00:00:03,830
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,830 --> 00:00:07,130
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make 
sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,130 --> 00:00:09,200
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:18,840 --> 00:00:21,160
Ouch! Ouchy, ouch!

5
00:00:22,850 --> 00:00:23,630
Gray!

6
00:00:23,630 --> 00:00:25,040
Got it!

7
00:00:25,040 --> 00:00:26,170
There!

8
00:00:26,170 --> 00:00:27,950
Please lemme off!

9
00:00:28,380 --> 00:00:30,870
You're the one who said he wanted to ride!

10
00:00:51,220 --> 00:00:55,630
It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.

11
00:00:55,630 --> 00:01:00,700
I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.

12
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:03,050
The intersection of all people

13
00:01:03,050 --> 00:01:05,660
whose dreams have come true is one point:

14
00:01:05,660 --> 00:01:10,290
Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!

15
00:01:10,290 --> 00:01:15,470
When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,

16
00:01:15,470 --> 00:01:17,620
grasp this hand, try to take a chance.

17
00:01:17,620 --> 00:01:20,890
Because you're not alone anymore, got it?

18
00:01:24,010 --> 00:01:26,000
Go forward, more and more!

19
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:28,520
Don't give up on your awesome dream!

20
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:29,780
That's right, don't cry!

21
00:01:29,780 --> 00:01:31,250
Move on, my way!

22
00:01:31,250 --> 00:01:33,630
Now, with the light shining down upon you.

23
00:01:33,630 --> 00:01:35,710
Don't even think about something like giving up!

24
00:01:35,710 --> 00:01:38,140
Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.

25
00:01:38,140 --> 00:01:43,630
Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,

26
00:01:43,630 --> 00:01:47,910
can surely see the light!

27
00:02:12,420 --> 00:02:15,650
This is Akane Resort.

28
00:02:15,650 --> 00:02:19,950
It's the most popular tourist spot in the Kingdom, located by the sea.

29
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:25,200
There's a giant amusement park and a five-star hotel next door.

30
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:29,790
There's a beach which will keep you coming back again and again.

31
00:02:30,620 --> 00:02:35,130
And then there's the sea expanding out to the infinite horizon...

32
00:02:36,100 --> 00:02:38,370
Using the tickets they received from Loke,

33
00:02:38,370 --> 00:02:44,010
Natsu and the others are visiting and having some excellent time off.

34
00:02:45,140 --> 00:02:46,810
Give me back my boxers!

35
00:02:46,810 --> 00:02:48,390
Not on your life!

36
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,100
I said, "Don't use Happy to cover yourself up!"

37
00:02:51,350 --> 00:02:53,940
Gray-sama... So bold!

38
00:02:56,730 --> 00:02:58,440
The Tower of Heaven!

39
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:15,350
But today sure was fun...

40
00:03:16,850 --> 00:03:18,040
Really...

41
00:04:13,270 --> 00:04:14,230
Erza...

42
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:17,680
There is no such thing as freedom in this world...

43
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:35,040
A dream?

44
00:04:37,810 --> 00:04:41,420
When did I fall asleep?

45
00:05:10,590 --> 00:05:13,090
I really do feel more at ease while I'm in armor.

46
00:05:14,140 --> 00:05:17,550
There's no help for a woman like me...

47
00:05:19,370 --> 00:05:20,420
Erza!

48
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:22,610
Want to go have some fun downstairs?

49
00:05:22,610 --> 00:05:24,690
Natsu and Gray are already down there.

50
00:05:24,690 --> 00:05:26,240
They wanted to go win some games!

51
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,930
Oh, yes! They have a place like that, don't they?

52
00:05:29,050 --> 00:05:30,340
In that case...

53
00:05:42,420 --> 00:05:44,260
Do I look the part?

54
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:47,480
Um, maybe that's a little <i>too</i> flashy...

55
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,410
Whatever...

56
00:05:48,660 --> 00:05:50,610
Let's go, Erza!

57
00:05:52,370 --> 00:05:57,060
Sometimes taking a day to pamper myself... isn't such a bad thing.

58
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:17,750
17! Come on, 17!

59
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:19,600
You can do it, 17!

60
00:06:23,660 --> 00:06:25,470
There's 17!

61
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:29,120
You've got to be kiddin' me!

62
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,680
17!

63
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:32,850
Sir, please refrain from...

64
00:06:32,850 --> 00:06:35,550
But it stopped on 17 once!

65
00:06:35,550 --> 00:06:36,550
It's so cruel!

66
00:06:36,550 --> 00:06:38,140
17!

67
00:06:38,140 --> 00:06:39,370
Crying isn't going to...

68
00:06:39,370 --> 00:06:42,380
Go back to 17!

69
00:06:42,380 --> 00:06:45,180
Sheesh, they're so immature.

70
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:46,590
Gray-sama...

71
00:06:50,250 --> 00:06:52,770
Juvia is here.

72
00:06:52,770 --> 00:06:54,390
You're that Phantom woman!

73
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:56,600
17! Come back now!

74
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,480
Sir, please stop.

75
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,890
Hold it, boy.

76
00:07:01,750 --> 00:07:05,480
Casinos are places for grownups... For dandies! Get it?

77
00:07:07,030 --> 00:07:08,630
Blocky!

78
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:12,010
Boy, let me tell you something.

79
00:07:12,010 --> 00:07:15,290
There's only two paths that men can travel.

80
00:07:15,290 --> 00:07:16,460
Huh?

81
00:07:18,580 --> 00:07:19,870
Who are you?

82
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:21,200
Natsu!

83
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:23,080
Live on as a dandy...

84
00:07:27,570 --> 00:07:30,500
Or stop and meet your end. Get it?

85
00:07:31,370 --> 00:07:34,910
I heard that Phantom was disbanded.

86
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:39,060
Yes. Juvia is now a Free Wizard.

87
00:07:41,420 --> 00:07:44,380
So I take it you want to join Fairy Tail, then?

88
00:07:44,380 --> 00:07:46,310
Yes, Juvia does!

89
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:49,300
But after all that...

90
00:07:49,300 --> 00:07:52,550
Well, I don't mind, but I'm not sure what the master would say.

91
00:07:52,550 --> 00:07:54,410
Juvia will do anything!

92
00:07:54,660 --> 00:07:57,120
I wouldn't say that so lightly if I were you.

93
00:07:57,610 --> 00:07:59,350
Gray Fullbuster?

94
00:08:07,970 --> 00:08:09,210
What's all the noise?

95
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:12,190
I guess the parade has started outside.

96
00:08:12,190 --> 00:08:13,130
...he says.

97
00:08:13,130 --> 00:08:14,050
Right.

98
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:16,210
Juvia!

99
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:18,420
Why, you...

100
00:08:18,420 --> 00:08:19,600
Who the hell are you?

101
00:08:19,930 --> 00:08:21,640
Where is Erza?

102
00:08:22,260 --> 00:08:23,120
Get it?

103
00:08:23,950 --> 00:08:25,180
What?

104
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,140
A straight!

105
00:08:28,140 --> 00:08:29,760
Awesome, Erza!

106
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,950
I'm really on a roll today.

107
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:35,430
Dealer change.

108
00:08:35,430 --> 00:08:36,810
R-Right...

109
00:08:37,950 --> 00:08:41,290
I have a feeling that I won't lose no matter who I'm up against.

110
00:08:41,290 --> 00:08:42,340
Yup!

111
00:08:43,510 --> 00:08:47,540
Then... why don't we play a special game?

112
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:56,720
Let's play a game where your life's on the line, Erza-neesan...

113
00:08:57,530 --> 00:09:00,860
You're... Sho?

114
00:09:00,860 --> 00:09:02,060
Sho, right?

115
00:09:02,380 --> 00:09:04,730
It's been quite a while, Sister.

116
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:06,540
Sister?

117
00:09:06,540 --> 00:09:08,860
You were... safe?

118
00:09:09,210 --> 00:09:10,580
Safe?

119
00:09:11,060 --> 00:09:13,110
Uh, well...

120
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:15,150
Erza...

121
00:09:15,820 --> 00:09:17,780
Where is Erza?

122
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:20,310
You think I'll tell you?

123
00:09:23,660 --> 00:09:27,130
I will not allow you to lay a finger on Gray-sama.

124
00:09:27,130 --> 00:09:29,110
Juvia will be your opponent.

125
00:09:29,110 --> 00:09:30,250
Juvia...

126
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:34,340
Danger is closing in around Erza-san.

127
00:09:34,340 --> 00:09:35,470
Sure looks like it.

128
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,760
What? You found her already?

129
00:09:41,340 --> 00:09:43,060
Oh, I see...

130
00:09:43,060 --> 00:09:45,680
So I can clean up here? Understood.

131
00:09:46,690 --> 00:09:48,480
Whoa, it went dark!

132
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,770
It's Dark Lineage Magic.

133
00:09:51,610 --> 00:09:53,390
Dark Moment.

134
00:09:54,980 --> 00:09:57,760
What's going on? I can't see a thing!

135
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:59,320
Natsu, where are you?

136
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,800
I'm here! But... where's here?

137
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:04,160
Good night, boy...

138
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:06,310
Don't give me that, you...

139
00:10:06,310 --> 00:10:08,310
Natsu!

140
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,070
A gunshot?

141
00:10:10,070 --> 00:10:11,110
What's happened?

142
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,590
Sho!

143
00:10:14,590 --> 00:10:15,170
Huh?

144
00:10:15,670 --> 00:10:17,550
Over here, Sister.

145
00:10:26,180 --> 00:10:27,320
That's...

146
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:29,160
The people are in the cards!

147
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,860
Help me!

148
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:31,730
Intrigued?

149
00:10:31,980 --> 00:10:33,000
Magic...

150
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:37,020
Yes. I can use it now too, Sister.

151
00:10:37,020 --> 00:10:38,360
You... What have you...

152
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:43,830
Lucy!

153
00:10:44,570 --> 00:10:46,740
Feelin' chip an' dipper?

154
00:10:46,740 --> 00:10:50,070
Milliana... You can use magic too?

155
00:10:50,070 --> 00:10:52,290
How's it been, Er-chan!

156
00:10:52,290 --> 00:10:55,560
Let Lucy go! She's my friend!

157
00:10:56,180 --> 00:10:57,900
Friend?

158
00:10:57,900 --> 00:11:00,680
We were your friends too once... Isn't that right, Sister?

159
00:11:00,990 --> 00:11:02,760
You were friends...?

160
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:06,180
We were, remember?

161
00:11:07,020 --> 00:11:10,690
That is... until you betrayed us, Sister.

162
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:16,090
Don't abuse Erza so much, Sho.

163
00:11:18,070 --> 00:11:21,570
A man who's a dandy should keep his emotions in check.

164
00:11:22,140 --> 00:11:23,070
What a blockhead!

165
00:11:23,430 --> 00:11:24,790
Long time no see!

166
00:11:24,790 --> 00:11:27,340
You grew a pretty hot body there.

167
00:11:27,610 --> 00:11:30,360
Are you... Wally?

168
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:32,680
I suppose it's not surprising you wouldn't recognize me.

169
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:36,060
Back then, when I was called "Mad Dog Wally,"

170
00:11:36,060 --> 00:11:39,930
I was a lot more... rough around the edges.

171
00:11:42,190 --> 00:11:44,070
You also use magic?

172
00:11:44,070 --> 00:11:45,760
You shouldn't be surprised.

173
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:49,620
Once you get the hang of it, anyone can use magic.

174
00:11:49,620 --> 00:11:51,310
Isn't that right, Erza?

175
00:11:51,310 --> 00:11:52,520
Simon...

176
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:56,610
Erza, who are these people?

177
00:11:56,610 --> 00:11:58,670
And why are they calling you their sister?

178
00:12:01,610 --> 00:12:03,580
I'm not actually their sister.

179
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:05,660
We were all together in the past.

180
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:07,690
Together?

181
00:12:07,690 --> 00:12:11,180
But haven't you been in Fairy Tail since you were really young?

182
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:13,370
It was before that.

183
00:12:15,100 --> 00:12:17,430
Why are you here?

184
00:12:17,430 --> 00:12:18,510
Why?

185
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:20,690
To take you back.

186
00:12:21,020 --> 00:12:23,950
Release Lucy!

187
00:12:24,350 --> 00:12:28,470
How about we go home, Sister?

188
00:12:28,470 --> 00:12:31,390
Unless you do what we say...

189
00:12:33,270 --> 00:12:35,700
Stop it, please!

190
00:12:36,230 --> 00:12:37,310
Don't!

191
00:12:40,270 --> 00:12:41,770
Erza!

192
00:12:41,770 --> 00:12:43,490
Erza!

193
00:12:54,990 --> 00:12:56,570
We've recovered our objective.

194
00:12:56,570 --> 00:12:57,570
Let us return home.

195
00:12:57,570 --> 00:12:58,910
You did it the right way?

196
00:12:58,910 --> 00:13:00,720
I used a tranquilizer shot.

197
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:03,680
Hey, where are you taking Erza?

198
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:05,010
Give her back!

199
00:13:05,010 --> 00:13:11,350
If you guys were up against Natsu or Gray they'd blow you away real quick!

200
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:15,440
Sorry, but they're the ones that got blown away.

201
00:13:15,820 --> 00:13:17,960
They were overrated.

202
00:13:18,670 --> 00:13:20,480
N-No...

203
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:22,190
Then they're...

204
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:24,660
As you imagine.

205
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:36,210
In another five minutes your body'll be completely bent backwards.

206
00:13:36,970 --> 00:13:40,520
Speaking of which, Milliana, I have a present for you.

207
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:44,710
It's a kitty-cat!

208
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,410
I'm so glad!

209
00:13:46,410 --> 00:13:47,360
Happy!

210
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:49,940
Milliana, bind Erza.

211
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:53,120
A kitty-cat!

212
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:53,840
Milliana, we're counting on you.

213
00:13:56,570 --> 00:13:57,720
Sister...

214
00:13:58,880 --> 00:14:02,440
You're coming back... to the Tower of Heaven!

215
00:14:03,930 --> 00:14:06,910
I just know that Jellal will be pleased!

216
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:11,290
The Tower of Heaven...

217
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:14,790
T-They finished it?

218
00:14:16,130 --> 00:14:17,350
Erza...

219
00:14:18,450 --> 00:14:19,960
Erza!

220
00:14:22,220 --> 00:14:23,460
Erza.

221
00:14:25,210 --> 00:14:29,970
Argh, I'm gonna bust outta this thing!

222
00:14:30,980 --> 00:14:32,370
All right!

223
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,430
Gate of the Giant Crab, I open thee!

224
00:14:37,430 --> 00:14:38,230
Cancer!

225
00:14:45,580 --> 00:14:46,230
Huh?

226
00:14:46,230 --> 00:14:47,620
Cancer?

227
00:14:47,620 --> 00:14:50,730
What? Then, Taurus!

228
00:14:50,730 --> 00:14:51,590
Loke!

229
00:14:51,590 --> 00:14:53,450
Come out!

230
00:14:56,070 --> 00:15:00,290
I can't use magic... Is it because of this rope?

231
00:15:00,290 --> 00:15:02,580
Ow! What is it now?

232
00:15:02,580 --> 00:15:04,370
Oh, I'm sorry.

233
00:15:04,370 --> 00:15:06,380
Wait, was that you?

234
00:15:06,380 --> 00:15:12,300
Yeah, see, since I can't get out, I was trying to prick it with this paper knife.

235
00:15:12,300 --> 00:15:14,510
Looks like I hit you.

236
00:15:15,030 --> 00:15:16,150
I'll try it too!

237
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:17,840
We might be able to get free!

238
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:21,130
The knife from inside the card poked me?

239
00:15:21,130 --> 00:15:21,900
Close-up!

240
00:15:21,900 --> 00:15:28,350
Hey, I don't know why, but that means that stuff from inside the card can affect the outside!

241
00:15:28,350 --> 00:15:29,490
I'm not sure.

242
00:15:29,490 --> 00:15:33,200
Then does my knife look like it's sticking out?

243
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:34,980
No, it's still flat.

244
00:15:34,980 --> 00:15:39,380
But if I felt pain, then its force can be felt outside!

245
00:15:40,020 --> 00:15:43,520
Please! Trying cutting my rope with that knife!

246
00:15:43,520 --> 00:15:45,170
Okay, I'll try.

247
00:15:49,290 --> 00:15:50,640
Hurry!

248
00:15:50,640 --> 00:15:52,450
Please don't rush me.

249
00:15:52,450 --> 00:15:54,090
Whatever, just get on with it!

250
00:15:55,170 --> 00:15:57,170
All right, they're cut!

251
00:15:58,570 --> 00:16:00,530
Thanks! You saved me!

252
00:16:00,530 --> 00:16:02,080
It was my pleasure.

253
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:04,080
Next, it's your turn to...

254
00:16:04,810 --> 00:16:07,190
Sorry! I'll come back and save you, I promise!

255
00:16:07,190 --> 00:16:08,510
Okay!

256
00:16:10,180 --> 00:16:13,990
Natsu, Gray... They're fine, right?

257
00:16:16,990 --> 00:16:19,450
Gray... No!

258
00:16:19,450 --> 00:16:21,900
Hey, get a hold of yourself!

259
00:16:22,580 --> 00:16:24,500
H-He's cold...

260
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:32,000
I-I-It'll be okay!

261
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:33,420
I'll fix you up, promise!

262
00:16:35,930 --> 00:16:37,980
Please stay calm.

263
00:16:41,460 --> 00:16:43,750
It's you, one of the Element 4!

264
00:16:43,750 --> 00:16:45,280
Wait, Lucy!

265
00:16:46,400 --> 00:16:48,790
She's not our enemy anymore.

266
00:16:48,790 --> 00:16:50,150
That is correct.

267
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:53,350
Gray-sama was inside of Juvia.

268
00:16:53,350 --> 00:16:55,050
I-Inside?

269
00:16:55,490 --> 00:16:58,890
Not inside of you... Inside of Juvia!

270
00:16:58,890 --> 00:17:00,450
Yes, that is true.

271
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:06,560
After it got dark all of a sudden, I figured I'd leave a double and see how things turned out, but...

272
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:12,610
In order for him not to be discovered by the enemy, Juvia protected Gray-sama in her Water Lock.

273
00:17:12,610 --> 00:17:16,230
And thanks to your meddling, he got away!

274
00:17:17,210 --> 00:17:19,770
Lucy, where's Natsu and the others?

275
00:17:19,770 --> 00:17:23,390
I don't know about Natsu, but Happy and Erza have been...

276
00:17:27,020 --> 00:17:28,310
Natsu!

277
00:17:29,420 --> 00:17:30,730
What a creep!

278
00:17:30,730 --> 00:17:31,910
Natsu!

279
00:17:32,890 --> 00:17:34,150
Did something happen?

280
00:17:34,150 --> 00:17:37,240
Is it normal to go shooting people in the mouth?

281
00:17:37,650 --> 00:17:38,790
That hurt!

282
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:40,590
A guy could get hurt really bad!

283
00:17:40,590 --> 00:17:44,540
Um, normal people would be totally KOed.

284
00:17:44,540 --> 00:17:46,040
Such is the Salamander.

285
00:17:46,040 --> 00:17:48,290
That damn blockhead!

286
00:17:48,540 --> 00:17:50,730
I won't let him escape!

287
00:17:50,730 --> 00:17:51,550
After him!

288
00:17:51,550 --> 00:17:53,630
Sure, but where did they go?

289
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:57,140
He's got a nose on him that'd put animals to shame.

290
00:17:58,800 --> 00:18:04,430
Blockhead!

291
00:18:41,970 --> 00:18:48,770
Lord Jellal, I'm here to report that they've captured Erza and are heading here now.

292
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:52,020
However...

293
00:18:52,270 --> 00:18:54,640
Why have you let that traitor live until now?

294
00:18:55,260 --> 00:18:59,400
With your magical power, you should have been able to dispose of her easily.

295
00:19:02,640 --> 00:19:04,470
Well, that wouldn't do.

296
00:19:04,470 --> 00:19:06,590
The world would be too boring a place.

297
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:14,640
However, now that the Tower of Heaven is complete, allowing her to live would cause issues.

298
00:19:15,020 --> 00:19:16,500
The time has come.

299
00:19:19,010 --> 00:19:24,410
You will become a living sacrifice to our aspiration, Erza Scarlet.

300
00:19:41,790 --> 00:19:42,810
Where am I?

301
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:46,520
Inside a ship, Sister.

302
00:19:46,940 --> 00:19:47,870
A ship?

303
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:53,370
Yes. Inside a ship heading toward the Tower of Heaven.

304
00:19:57,010 --> 00:19:59,630
Oh... So that's it.

305
00:20:00,250 --> 00:20:01,830
Will you untie me?

306
00:20:01,830 --> 00:20:03,330
I don't plan to resist.

307
00:20:03,620 --> 00:20:05,410
I can't do that.

308
00:20:05,410 --> 00:20:07,760
Because you're a traitor, Sister.

309
00:20:09,590 --> 00:20:14,080
It's pointless. Milliana's tubes have the power of sealing magic.

310
00:20:14,540 --> 00:20:17,070
You can't do anything about them on your own.

311
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:18,840
No matter how powerful you are, Sister.

312
00:20:22,010 --> 00:20:23,690
I-I know...

313
00:20:24,090 --> 00:20:28,220
Then would you at least allow me to requip into armor?

314
00:20:29,890 --> 00:20:33,910
I'm afraid... to return to that tower...

315
00:20:36,210 --> 00:20:40,650
Unless I'm wearing armor... the fear...

316
00:20:41,890 --> 00:20:44,990
But you look good in that dress, Sister.

317
00:20:52,270 --> 00:20:55,390
I didn't want to do this...

318
00:20:56,250 --> 00:20:57,590
Sho...

319
00:20:59,380 --> 00:21:02,820
I missed you! Really!

320
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:06,870
Sister!

321
00:21:07,950 --> 00:21:11,120
Why... did you...

322
00:21:11,700 --> 00:21:14,120
...betray Jellal!

323
00:21:20,360 --> 00:21:21,700
Jellal...

324
00:21:28,650 --> 00:21:31,060
Sis, over here, hurry!

325
00:21:31,060 --> 00:21:33,790
Sho, don't be so loud!

326
00:21:33,790 --> 00:21:36,490
You're even louder, Wally!

327
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:38,850
Sorry, Milliana.

328
00:21:39,100 --> 00:21:42,380
Erza, if we don't hurry, they'll find us.

329
00:21:43,560 --> 00:21:44,280
Right.

330
00:21:44,940 --> 00:21:48,740
But, if they find out...

331
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:55,170
I know... What they do to the kids that are found out...

332
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:58,920
Don't worry, there's nothing to be afraid of.

333
00:21:59,780 --> 00:22:01,690
J-Jellal!

334
00:22:03,220 --> 00:22:06,090
We're going to get our freedom.

335
00:22:06,790 --> 00:22:09,010
Our future, and our aspirations.

336
00:22:14,980 --> 00:22:17,020
Let's go, Erza!

337
00:22:18,460 --> 00:22:19,280
Yeah!

338
00:23:56,150 --> 00:24:00,280
Since Happy's been kidnapped, this time I'm doin' the preview all by myself!

339
00:24:00,280 --> 00:24:04,370
So, calling to order the first "Plan to Save Happy and Erza" meeting!

340
00:24:04,370 --> 00:24:05,770
The plan is simple.

341
00:24:05,770 --> 00:24:08,730
Barge in through the front door and blow away the enemy!

342
00:24:08,730 --> 00:24:11,250
The codename is "CHARGE!"

343
00:24:11,250 --> 00:24:13,510
All right, let's do this!

344
00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:16,470
Next time: Jellal!

345
00:24:16,470 --> 00:24:18,860
Wait, Happy... Why are you...

346
00:24:19,180 --> 00:24:21,460
You'll understand when you're older.

347
00:24:21,460 --> 00:24:23,920
What? That doesn't make any sense.

